9036651_1318682486169620_6921811442815663041_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Dzodc_DSD4EQ7kNvgG3x3vY&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDQFu9OtI0Sb2k5bPXI_rn4979k9selQhN3T41kAomRoQ&oe=6717A421"}, "display_name": "Spinball", "keywords": ["Tennis", "Racket", "Ball", "Spikeball", "Pong"], "long_description": "# \ud83e\udd4e Welcome to Spinball!\n\nExperience the thrill of a brand-new mixed-reality ball game right in your own living room. \n\n# \ud83e\udd4eStep into the ring and compete against players from around the world in epic 1v1 racket battles!\n{574323518497639}\n\n# \ud83e\udd4eFace Sparx the AI bot in multiple difficulty levels\n{504858232438242}\n\n# \ud83e\udd4eTest your skills and improve your game with the Spinball ball machine!\n{542434168331966}\n\n# \ud83e\udd4ePlay minigames to improve your skill in the Spinball Academy\n{1046764560002561}\n\n# \ud83e\udd4eCustomize your equipment in the locker room, climb the ranks, and become a Spinball All-Star.\n{2471607009895811}\n\n**Main features:**\n* Online ranked/unranked game modes\n* Solo mode - Face Sparx in multiple difficulty AI levels\n* Spinball Academy - Multiple training modes\n* Spinball Friends - Add and invite your friends for private matches\n* Main Locker - Customize your rackets, balls and characters", "short_description": "Welcome to Spinball!\n\nExperience the thrill of a brand-new mixed-reality ball game right in your own living room. \n\nStep into the ring and compete against players from around the world in epic 1v1 racket battles!\n\nPlay online and make your way to the top of the online leagues, go up against your friends for private matches and customize your rackets, balls and characters in the Spinball Locker!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.blue-duck-studios.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Blue Duck Studios", "support_website_url": "https://www.blue-duck-studios.com/",